RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2008-2133 and 2008-2228. State v. Underwood.

Montgomery App. No. 22454, 2008-Ohio-4748. Reported at 124 Ohio St.3d 365, 2010-Ohio-1, 922 N.E.2d 923. On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.
